        From the Manufacturer

        Great Atelier.Never forget this adventure.

        This work is a new "Atelier" series based on the concept of "a little growth of a life-size boy or girl."

        Everyone is in the memory of a special friend for each and every one.

        The story of Lyza is that they find something important to themselves before they become grown up.

        We are into a new world of "Atelier" with light, shadows and breathing of the world.

        In order to illustrate the theme of this work, the story of the protagonist of life size, the field also has been recreated using the shadows of nature, so that the field can feel the breath of the world.

        In addition, the fantasy expression unique to the "Atelier" series has also been further enhanced, so you can immerse yourself in the new "Atelier" world regardless of the new or old.

        A new expressive world of everyday and adventure

        Part of this field map There are many situations where you can feel the spread of adventure.

        Introducing an improved formulation system & new "Creu"

        This product has been renewed into the Formulation system that combines ingredients to create items that are familiar with the Atelier series.

        It will help you see the visually mixing instructions and transform the fun of recipe development.

        In addition, there is a new system to "create" items that you have never created before.Expect for continued report

        Active harvesting

        "Harvest" to get the ingredients of the formula.

        This product turns passive picking into a more active retrieve.

        Even at the same point of picking up the items that can be harvested depending on the selected picking tool.

        A tight combat.

        Unlike traditional turn command systems, you can enjoy the intense battle created by dynamic selection of action.

        It also has a system that allows you to feel stronger bonds with friends.

        The protagonist is a girl looking for something to escape the daily life.

        The protagonist Lisa is an ordinary girl who is everywhere.

        When you feel anxious in the life of a boring village, gathering with uncomforting friends, they told their dreams, and plan out out of the village for stimulation.

        One day, Risers woken up for their first exploration to the "Conspicuous Islands" that are forbidden to stand in.

        With his companions, Ryzas came to the "opshore".

        So she greeted a fate "encounter" that changes her daily life.

        How are ratings calculated?
        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.
